  "instructions": [
    "Heat sunflower oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and coriander seeds. Let them sizzle for a minute.",
    "Add chopped onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Add minced garlic and sauté for another minute.",
    "Add Dutch curry powder, chili powder, and turmeric. Mix well.",
    "Add ginger paste and mix well.",
    "Add brown rice and mix well.",
    "Add water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and cook for 20 minutes or until the rice is cooked.",
    "While the rice cooks, heat some oil in a separate pan and fry chopped onion until caramelized.",
    "Add cumin seeds and coriander seeds to the pan and mix well."
